snippet.title: CHAMP Pac-em gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for CHAMP Pac-em, Dos PC game produced by CHAMProgramming in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/champ-pac-em/8438/
Gobbling pills and ghosts in this update to the classic arcade game.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
